  "text": "where η x i , η d m and η u n denote the virtual prices of inputs, desirable outputs, and undesirable outputs, respectively. Let p j denote the market price of the j-th output. In our case, we use electricity produced by thermal electricity generation as the \"numeraire\" output. Following Wei et al. [CITATION_1] , we can then use the virtual prices yielded by the above model to count the shadow prices of undesirable output p u via:",
